## Core Protocols (MANDATORY)
- **Multi-Agent Delivery**: `dev/ai/rules/multi-agent-protocol.md` (HIGHEST PRIORITY)
- **Agent Supervisor**: `dev/ai/rules/agent-supervisor-protocol.md` (when you see @AgentID markers)
- **Quality System**: `dev/ai/rules/QUALITY_SYSTEM_CURSOR_RULES.md`
- **Efficiency Rules**: `dev/ai/rules/efficiency_rules.md`

## Critical Constraints
- NEVER edit `generated/` directory
- NEVER use `routes.xml` (routing is auto-discovered)
- NEVER use JS `alert()/confirm()` (use BackendToast/BackendConfirm)
- ALWAYS use i18n: `__('text')` or `<lang>text</lang>`
- ALWAYS end ORM chains with `.fetch()` or `.fetchArray()`

## Commands
```bash
php bin/w setup:upgrade [--route]  # Schema/route sync
php bin/w http:request / [-b|-api] # Route test
php bin/w server:reload|restart -r # WLS lifecycle
```

